verbs.description: The Trump administration [V: has] stirred conflict with some of America 's oldest allies with tariffs on all US steel and aluminum imports . Europeans , Canadians and Mexicans buy more American goods and services than anyone else in the world . Disrupting US – Canada trade could affect NAFTA - era supply chains .
